'''[[Bastille]] [[day|Day]]'''

#The [[French]] national [[holiday]] celebrated on 14 [[July]] each year. It commemorates the 1790 Fête de la Fédération, held on the first [[anniversary]] of the [[storm]]ing of the [[Bastille]] on 14 July 1789; the Fête de la Fédération was seen as a [[symbol]] of the [[uprising]] of the modern French "nation".

